name: Haeundae Rib Barbeque Restaurant
description: Since opening in 1964, Haeundae Amsogalbijip has proudly served the finest Korean beef short ribs, both in their pure form and marinated with our special recipe. Our signature touch, a unique potato noodle, enhances the experience. The signature diamond cut, which softens the beef’s texture, was invented by our first-generation founder, the late Chairman Yoon Seok-ho, in 1964 and is still crafted in the same way today. Unlike others, we don’t use machines to prepare our beef; though it’s labor-intensive, the difference in texture is worth every effort, so we continue to prepare each piece by hand. We hope our restaurant becomes a place for guests to relive the past and embrace new memories for the future. Beyond just a meal, we want this to be a moment that brings good feelings. We’re always here, ready to offer you a dining experience with heartfelt dedication, making sure each meal brings joy.
